58
00:03:44.300 --> 00:03:46.530
Why would he bribe anyone to commit arson?

59
00:03:46.530 --> 00:03:50.250
Someone else was profiting from those fires.

60
00:03:52.040 --> 00:03:56.290
Enter the man who sold the wood
for rebuilding those houses:

61
00:03:56.290 --> 00:03:58.250
That would be Bongo.

